# Fix x86-64 ELF static linker

> Debug and repair an existing single-file C static linker (myld.c) for x86-64 Linux so that the ELF executables it produces actually run correctly. Must handle .o objects and .a archives, resolve symbols, merge sections, apply relocations, and support both minimal-runtime and musl libc test programs.

---

